data.description: Completely remodeled home - plumbing, HVAC, electrical, and flooring. Step inside to lovely vinyl wood floors throughout the downstairs living areas. Flex room right inside would make a great formal living, formal dining, home office, playroom, you name it! Second spacious living area toward the back of the house. Enjoy the updated kitchen with quartz counters, SS appliances including an apron front farm sink, tile backsplash, and on-trend painted cabinets. Full bath downstairs has a walk-in tiled shower. All bedrooms upstairs for convenience! Some of the spacious and bright bedrooms have barn door closet doors for added charm. Full bath upstairs is updated with a walk-in shower. Enjoy lots of natural light throughout as well as recessed lighting. Don't miss the fully fenced backyard with lots of green space! With a walkability score of 83, shopping and dining is just outside your door as well as the beach and Galveston's Pleasure Pier!
